## Project Introduction

Home Bites is a digital catalog platform designed to support home-based family businesses by allowing them to showcase their homemade food online.

The system enables customers to:
- Browse available dishes  
- View prices and descriptions  
- Contact the family directly via WhatsApp to place orders  

The platform focuses on food discovery and communication, while the transaction process is handled externally through WhatsApp.

